dashboardMetadata.name: ðŸ’² Risk Revenue Analysis By Member Status

tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: select sum(doubleProperties.bookingtotal) as "Platinum Revenue" FROM usersession where useraction.name = "Finish" and stringProperties.membershipstatus="Platinum"and (useraction.apdexCategory ="TOLERATING" or useraction.apdexCategory ="FRUSTRATED" or useraction.apdexCategory ="UNKNOWN")

tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: select DISTINCT DATETIME(starttime, "HH:mm", "10m") as "Time", sum(doubleProperties.bookingtotal) as "Platinum Revenue" FROM usersession where useraction.name = "Finish" and doubleProperties.bookingtotal>0  and stringProperties.membershipstatus="Platinum"and (useraction.apdexCategory ="TOLERATING" or useraction.apdexCategory ="FRUSTRATED" or useraction.apdexCategory ="UNKNOWN")
